{"tid":1147234,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[新] 95~99 9up谷收人！入黎識真心朋友喇喂～","createTime":"2019-05-09T17:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T15:26:19.000Z","uid":144683,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2bfb3834e2688930a24443a308fcff31889bbdd9","tid":1147234,"uid":144683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T17:44:46.000Z","msg":"歡迎大家入黎傾下計熱鬧下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好比個谷靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n預計周不時都會搞好多聚會<br />\n例如 打機 飯聚 唱K 行街shopping 飲野 bbq 踩單車 乜活動都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地大部份人都好得閒<br />\n入黎肯出聲就一定會覆你陪你9up 吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有感情問題我地都有經驗豐富嘅谷友開解你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對新人仲會好好添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宗旨都係想大家出到社會識唔到朋友<br />\n可以比大家一個谷識到可能做到一世嘅好朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚴禁5p仔厹入黎搵sp食女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更加嚴禁娘娘入黎玩感情收兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一經發現或收到舉報唔會通知即踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外為咗唔想絲打出到黎聚驚冇女仔陪<br />\n巴打又唔想一齊格劍嘅話<br />\n我地男女比例會平衡返小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未入到嘅請耐心等候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfiXcpIKDmRDMVGx1VNgVBMsBW1EliETnUMcDFRe-tB_AJ4Yw/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfiXcpIKDmRDMVGx1VNgVBMsBW1EliETnUMcDFRe-tB_AJ4Yw%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGi%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=b0d784fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfiXcpIKDmRDMVGx1VNgVBMsBW1EliETnUMcDFRe-tB_AJ4Yw/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n想加入嘅巴絲打請填一填先<br />\n我地有專人on call check名單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後由於假人太多<br />\n冇icon嘅會低啲機會入到㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望下一個朋友係認識到你"},{"pid":"6928e35489de5c352185510517f3b6b7310b05b0","tid":1147234,"uid":144683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T19:13:04.000Z","msg":"深夜一推"},{"pid":"c1cfa2844a1cbf90df4e9714c5f385ceb7cd8d0b","tid":1147234,"uid":144982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T22:39:29.000Z","msg":"好似填咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d740643351f19aab0e2b66f4e11eb269941d7a","tid":1147234,"uid":144683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T03:21:04.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"63d1186d0aac2554387e8b035aed6f558ec186cf","tid":1147234,"uid":144683,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"c1cfa2844a1cbf90df4e9714c5f385ceb7cd8d0b","tid":1147234,"uid":144982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T22:39:29.000Z","msg":"好似填咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T03:24:26.000Z","msg":"今日會加人㗎啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ed789a49427f29acd1821bc9877a927cc54745","tid":1147234,"uid":144683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:01:56.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"01bc441a2f8fd5096c27c0c39904ab931df3c483","tid":1147234,"uid":144683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T11:20:16.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"955c62c52a3cdb1c6dab69a78b8ab81148c4ad41","tid":1147234,"uid":144982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63d1186d0aac2554387e8b035aed6f558ec186cf","tid":1147234,"uid":144683,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"c1cfa2844a1cbf90df4e9714c5f385ceb7cd8d0b",